{"data":[{"date":"08:55 10/08","title":"M\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u00e2n binh, Alexis Sanchez ng\u1ea7m ch\u00ea MU \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1eb9p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/muon-tan-binh-alexis-sanchez-ngam-che-mu-da-khong-dep.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile t\u1ea5m t\u1eafc khen ng\u1ee3i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Fred s\u1ebd mang \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p v\u1ed1n \u0111ang tr\u1ed1ng v\u1eafng \u1edf Old Trafford.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">K\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac \u1edf Anh v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng d\u00e0nh cho Man Utd, khi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh n\u00e0o n\u1eefa trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung v\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alexis Sanchez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Fred c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Alexis Sanchez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Fred c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/muon-tan-binh-alexis-sanchez-ngam-che-mu-da-khong-dep.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Alexis Sanchez n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh Fred c\u1ee7a MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">V\u1edbi b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i v\u00f4 danh nh\u01b0 t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb Diogo Dalot hay th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb Lee Grant, Fred tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m 25 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh t\u1eeb Shakhtar Donetsk v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 52 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng t\u1ea7m tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n Old Trafford trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n Fred c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9, khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Alexis Sanchez t\u1ea5m t\u1eafc khen ng\u1ee3i. Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile: \u201cFred \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho t\u00f4i v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng ch\u1ec9 qua nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 Andreas Pereira mang \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y \u2018jogo bonito\u2019 \u2013 th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1eb9p trong ti\u1ebfng Brazil hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng \u1edf MU.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 nh\u1ebd Alexis Sanchez \u0111ang c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u00e1 xo\u00e1y, ng\u1ea7m ch\u00ea bai ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi m\u1ed9t HLV n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng th\u1ef1c d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0 Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n, thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 ra sao trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m qua.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man Utd chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00f3 vinh d\u1ef1 khai m\u1ea1c Premier League 2018/19 v\u1edbi m\u00e0n ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Leicester City tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Old Trafford. M\u1ee5c ti\u00eau duy nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng cho m\u1ed9t kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi xua tan \u00e1p l\u1ef1c n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-mu-vs-leicester-2h00-ngay-118-van-su-khoi-dau-nan-172-194151.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/nhan-dinh-mu-vs-leicester-2h00-ngay-118-van-su-khoi-dau-nan.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-mu-vs-leicester-2h00-ngay-118-van-su-khoi-dau-nan-172-194151.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester (2h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8): V\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nan</span><br>\r\nC\u00e2u th\u00e0nh ng\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch B\u1ea7y C\u00e1o chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ecba Old Trafford c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Premier League. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i l\u00e0...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5310","checkdouble":"194148"},{"date":"07:45 10/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester (2h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8): V\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nan","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/nhan-dinh-mu-vs-leicester-2h00-ngay-118-van-su-khoi-dau-nan.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e2u th\u00e0nh ng\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng nhi\u00ean \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho v\u1ecb kh\u00e1ch B\u1ea7y C\u00e1o chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ecba Old Trafford c\u1ee7a nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Premier League. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i l\u00e0 n\u00f3 c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng sai \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau m\u1ed9t n\u0103m n\u00fap b\u00f3ng h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m Man City v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tr\u1eafng tay tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi m\u1eb7t tr\u1eadn, Man United h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng vang d\u1ed9i \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Tuy nhi\u00ean nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua trong h\u00e8, ngay c\u1ea3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong top 4 Premier League c\u0169ng \u0111ang b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester (2h00 ng\u00e0y 118) V\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester (2h00 ng\u00e0y 118) V\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Preview-Man-Utd-vs-Leicester.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 \u1edf M\u1ef9 kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i l\u00e0 t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p, khi Man Utd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t thi\u1ebfu s\u1ee9c s\u1ed1ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c, t\u1eeb li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a chi\u1ebfu d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn thua Bayer Munich hay \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t th\u1ea3m b\u1ea1i 1-4 d\u01b0\u1edbi tay \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Liverpool, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 xen gi\u1eefa c\u00f3 l\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u1ed9n b\u1ec1 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 r\u1ed1i ren t\u1eeb tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf \u0111\u1ebfn v\u00e0o trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00ean lu\u00f4n th\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ea7ng Old Trafford. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n hay th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9, tinh th\u1ea7n thi \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Jose Mourinho hi\u1ec7n c\u00f2n \u0111ang m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn, b\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh ban l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o MU v\u00e0 sau ng\u00e0y deadline 9/8 v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, n\u00f3 c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean \u0111\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 d\u1ea7n tr\u1edf n\u00ean \u201cc\u01a1m kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0nh, canh kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ecdt\u201d v\u1edbi ph\u00f3 ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Ed Woodward v\u00ec c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Man Utd trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. R\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 khi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ea1nh tranh \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua v\u0169 trang, \u1ea5y th\u1ebf r\u1ed3i Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u00f3n th\u00eam ba t\u00e2n binh, v\u1edbi hai trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u1ec9 ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester (2h00 ng\u00e0y 118) V\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester (2h00 ng\u00e0y 118) V\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/26/Nhan-dinh-MU-vs-Leicester-(2h00-ngay-118)-Van-su-khoi-dau-nan-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c lo ng\u1ea1i v\u1ec1 c\u00e1i g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 \u201cl\u1eddi nguy\u1ec1n\u201d m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 ba c\u1ee7a Mourinho khi \u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecb c\u00e1c CLB trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 sa th\u1ea3i v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y v\u00e0 ra \u0111i trong th\u1ebf c\u00fai \u0111\u1ea7u. Th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y khai m\u1ea1c Premier League khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Leicester tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1eadn m\u1ec7nh c\u1ee7a MU v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 HLV x\u1ee9 B\u1ed3 trong n\u0103m nay.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1ed9t m\u00f9a h\u00e8 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i y\u00ean \u1eafng khi\u1ebfn Man Utd g\u1eb7p kh\u00f4ng \u00edt kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh thi \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng hay ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe sung m\u00e3n nh\u1ea5t sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng Matic, Herrera, Rojo, Valencia hay t\u00e2n binh Dalot, trong khi nh\u1eefng Pogba, Lukaku, Lingard, Young hay Fellaini c\u0169ng b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n. Li\u1ec7u th\u00f3i quen kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p c\u00f3 l\u1ea1i cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi n\u00e0y?<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 may m\u1eafn cho h\u1ecd khi b\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Leicester tr\u00ean gi\u1ea5y t\u1edd c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1 kh\u1ea9m g\u00ec h\u01a1n. B\u1ea7y C\u00e1o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea3i qua m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 b\u1eadn r\u1ed9n v\u00e0 nh\u1ed9n nh\u1ecbp h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed chi ti\u00eau nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i cho h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn mang t\u00ean Riyad Marez.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Maguire cua Leicester\" title=\"Maguire cua Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/Harry-Maguire-muon-den-MU-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester v\u00f2ng 1 Premier League 2018/19</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Chia tay ng\u00f4i sao nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Algeria sang Man City v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, Leicester ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng suy y\u1ebfu tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y so v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ed3 chi \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh t\u1eebng \u0111\u0103ng quang ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ba m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. T\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng Rachid Ghezzal \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng, nh\u01b0ng anh c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f3n h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i t\u1eeb Monaco m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh nh\u1eefng tuy\u1ec3n Anh nh\u01b0 Jamie Vardy hay Harry Maguire v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 sung m\u00e3n sau khi h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, c\u00f2n b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 19 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u00c7a\u011flar S\u00f6y\u00fcnc\u00fc c\u00f3 l\u1ebd s\u1ebd ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 tr\u1ea1ng v\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd hay kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u00edch nghi \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ra s\u00e2n xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t ngay sau khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y deadline, Leicester s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ee7 m\u1ecdi r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i t\u1eeb tr\u00ean c\u00f4ng xu\u1ed1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1ee7 \u1edf Old Trafford.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">L\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u0169ng \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 B\u1ea7y C\u00e1o khi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thua 6/6 tr\u1eadn g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y nh\u1ea5t khi \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Man Utd. V\u1eady n\u00ean, m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1m xua tan m\u00e2y m\u00f9 \u1edf Old Trafford l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n trong t\u1ea7m tay c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Mourinho.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester:<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Man Utd (4-3-3): 1. De Gea; 36. Darmian \u2013 3. Bailly \u2013 12. Smalling \u2013 23. Shaw; 39. McTominay \u2013 17. Fred \u2013 15. Pereira; 8. Mata \u2013 10. Rashford \u2013 7. Sanchez<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Leicester (4-2-3-1): Schmeichel; Pereira \u2013 Morgan \u2013 Evans \u2013 Chilwell; Ndidi \u2013 Iborra, Diabate \u2013 Maddison \u2013 Albrighton; Iheanacho<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester (2h00 ng\u00e0y 118) V\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester (2h00 ng\u00e0y 118) V\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nan h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 4\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Nhan-dinh-MU-vs-Leicester-(2h00-ngay-118)-Van-su-khoi-dau-nan-hinh-anh-4.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester: 2-1<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-truoc-them-nha-201819-mou-mua-3-va-ket-cuc-buon-tham-172-193964.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/22/mu-truoc-them-nha-201819-mou-mua-3-va-ket-cuc-buon-tham.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-truoc-them-nha-201819-mou-mua-3-va-ket-cuc-buon-tham-172-193964.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc Premier League 2018/19: Mou m\u00f9a 3 v\u00e0 k\u1ebft c\u1ee5c bu\u1ed3n th\u1ea3m?</span><br>\r\nJose Mourinho th\u01b0\u1eddng kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ee5 n\u1ed5i \u1edf m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00e1 3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. V\u00e0 M.U tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m NHA 2018/19 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y d\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u t\u01b0\u01a1i s\u00e1ng n\u00e0o r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5309","checkdouble":"194151"},{"date":"08:47 10/08","title":"Ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U, Pogba c\u00f3 c\u00f2n h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/10/Pogba-va-Mourinho.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Paul Pogba h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i M.U. \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 tin ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p mu\u1ed1n \u0111i theo ti\u1ebfng g\u1ecdi c\u1ee7a Barcelona song \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pogba kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi M.U</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, Paul Pogba \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng trong ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 25 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i \u0110TQG c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c so v\u1edbi t\u1ea1i Man United. Anh tr\u1ea3i qua m\u00f9a 2017/18 b\u1ea5t \u1ed5n v\u00e0 h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nBarcelona \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn Pogba v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a anh. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3n r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi M.U \u0111\u1ec3 tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3. Juventus c\u0169ng c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Paul Pogba h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Paul Pogba h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/1/Mourinho-tiet-lo-Paul-Pogba-hanh-phuc-tai-MU-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Pogba trong m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng sau khi chi\u1ec1u mua t\u1ea1i Anh \u0111\u00f3ng l\u1ea1i, M.U v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng n\u00e0o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u1ecd s\u1ebd gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Pogba \u1edf l\u1ea1i trong \u00edt nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 n\u1eeda \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a 2018/19.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho tin Pogba h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paul Pogba h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i M.U, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a HLV Jose Mourinho. &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 2. C\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i l\u00e0 Pogba r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac, t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n&rdquo;, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i trong m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o. &ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong v\u00e0i ng\u00e0y qua.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pogba va Mourinho\" title=\"Pogba va Mourinho\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/Pogba-va-Mourinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mourinho ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 Paul Pogba h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u1ebf n\u00e0o c\u1ea3 v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c v\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c tr\u00f2 chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1edbi Ashley Young, Marouane Fellaini, Jesse Lingard. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n bi\u1ebft h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1edf tr\u1eadn t\u1edbi (v\u1edbi Leicester) hay kh\u00f4ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ea3i ph\u00e1p v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng m\u1ecdi ngu\u1ed3n l\u1ef1c. T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y Pogba r\u1ea5t \u1ed5n nh\u01b0ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 ch\u1ee9ng th\u1ef1c xem h\u1ecd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i m\u1ed9t tay hay kh\u00f4ng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng v\u00e0 t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a ngu\u1ed3n l\u1ef1c t\u1eeb m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5308","checkdouble":"194152"},{"date":"08:59 10/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: MU chia tay trung v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/10/chinh-thuc-fosumensah-roi-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sao tr\u1ebb Timothy Fosu-Mensah \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi MU v\u00e0 gia nh\u1eadp Fulham theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.</h2><h2>Fosu-Mensah l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi MU</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Fosu-Mensah \u0111\u00e3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Anh ra s\u00e2n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 c\u0169ng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Mourinho gi\u1eef l\u1ea1i m\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Fulham theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSao tr\u1ebb 20 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1ea1i Crystal Palace. \u1ede th\u00e0nh London, Fosu-Mensah \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 21 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Fosu-Mensah r\u1eddi MU theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Fosu-Mensah r\u1eddi MU theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/CHINH-THUC-Fosu-Mensah-roi-MU-theo-dang-cho-muon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Fosu-Mensah r\u1eddi MU \u0111\u1ebfn Fulham theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00e0 m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Fosu-Mensah l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London kh\u00e1c. Chia s\u1ebb sau khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Craven Cottage, Fosu-Mensah cho bi\u1ebft:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t v\u1ec1 CLB n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t. Fulham c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1ed1t cho s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV v\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u0169ng \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn cho t\u00f4i m\u1ed9t c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n n\u1eefa\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Fulham t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Tony Khan c\u1ee7a Fulham t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 vui m\u1eebng v\u1ec1 t\u00e2n binh v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 r\u1eb1ng Fulham \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Fosu-Mensah theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Man United. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ecb tr\u00ed kh\u00e1c nhau. V\u00e0 s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh t\u1ea1i Premier League\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Fulham \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Jean-Michael Seri, Maxime Le Marchand, Alfie Mawson, Fabri, Joe Bryan v\u00e0 Aleksandar Mitrovic theo d\u1ea1ng mua \u0111\u1ee9t b\u00e1n \u0111o\u1ea1n. Ngo\u00e0i ra, The Cottagers c\u00f2n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Andre Schurrle, Calum Chambers, Luciano Vietto v\u00e0 Sergio Rico theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/fosumensah-chung-chac-o-tuoi-18-172-131353.html\" target=\"_blank\">Fosu-Mensah \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n ra m\u1eaft Man United</span> \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2015/16. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y c\u00f2n 2 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 CLB\u00a0Man United:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/paul-pogba-hanh-phuc-tai-mu-172-194152.html\">Ph\u1ea3i \u1edf l\u1ea1i M.U, Pogba c\u00f3 c\u00f2n h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-mu-vs-leicester-2h00-ngay-118-van-su-khoi-dau-nan-172-194151.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh MU vs Leicester (2h00 ng\u00e0y 11/8): V\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u nan</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5307","checkdouble":"194154"},{"date":"19:09 09/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 09/08: \u201cHarry Maguire ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ebfn MU\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-0908-hlv-leicester-harry-magui-chac-chan-den-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 09/08.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Leicester: \u201cHarry Maguire ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ebfn MU\u201d</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 0908 Maguire \u0111\u1ebfn MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 0908 Maguire \u0111\u1ebfn MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/30/Diem-tin-Bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-0908-Maguire-den-MU-hinh-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Claude Puel kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Maguire s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn MU v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam mai</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, HLV Claude Puel kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ebfn MU: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd t\u1edbi Manchester, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Old Trafford 2 gi\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa M.U v\u00e0 Leicester \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19. Maguire s\u1ebd c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi\u00a0Leicester h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd\u201d.</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho ph\u1ea3n ph\u00e1o l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18. \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong th\u1eddi gian qua l\u00e0 phi l\u00fd: \u201c T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh 8 ch\u1ee9c V\u0110QG v\u00e0 3 t\u1ea1i gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n suy ngh\u0129 v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2 m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u01b0\u1ee1ng m\u1ed9 nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p.\u201d<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-mu-mua-giai-201718-172-194127.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-mu-mua-giai-201718.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mourinho-phat-bieu-ve-mu-mua-giai-201718-172-194127.html\">Mourinho: \u201cM.U \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 2 NHA ch\u1eb3ng kh\u00e1c g\u00ec\u2026 xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng\u201d</span><br>\r\nJose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 M.U m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18.  \u00d4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh trong th\u1eddi gian qua l\u00e0 phi l\u00fd.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Barca \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 Yerry Mina c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 34 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca b\u00e1n Yerry Mina cho Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 34 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Mail c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU t\u00ednh g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c v\u1edbi tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Atletico</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Diego Godin trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Jerome Boateng, Toby Alderweireld, Yerry Mina v\u00e0 Harry Maguire.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU v\u1eafng 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n g\u1eb7p Leicester</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 MU, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1ebd v\u1eafng 6 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Leicester trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng 1 Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>West Ham chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \"bom x\u1ecbt\" c\u1ee7a Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 0908 Harry Maguire ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ebfn MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 0908 Harry Maguire ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u1ebfn MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Diem-tin-Bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-0908-Harry-Maguire-chac-chan-den-MU-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>West Ham mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Perez</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">West Ham mua Lucas Perez th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Arsenal, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-west-ham-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-arsenal-172-194121.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/Diem-tin-Bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-0908-Harry-Maguire-chac-chan-den-MU-hinh-anh-2.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-west-ham-chieu-mo-thanh-cong-sao-arsenal-172-194121.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: West Ham chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng bom x\u1ecbt c\u1ee7a Arsenal</span><br>\r\nWest Ham mua Lucas Perez th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb Arsenal, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mourinho bi quan v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng mua th\u00eam ng\u01b0\u1eddi</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo b\u00e0i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, HLV Jose Mourinho chia s\u1ebb t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a MU, \u00f4ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n di\u1ec5n ra kh\u00f4ng thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\u00e0 Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u00eam t\u00e2n binh trong th\u1eddi gian c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u00edt \u1ecfi \u1edf phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>2 \u0111\u1ea1i gia Ligue 1 \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Barca</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ivan Rakitic r\u1eddi Barca, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 PSG v\u00e0 Monaco. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Ligue 1 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi \u0111\u1eadm mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>V\u1eeba sang Chelsea, bom t\u1ea5n 71 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 m\u01a1 l\u00e0m huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Chelea, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Kepa kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cT\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n gi\u00fap CLB gi\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u1ee7a Chelsea\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real n\u00edu k\u00e9o Modric \u1edf l\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o c\u1ee7a Inter</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Luka Modric\" title=\"Luka Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/7/real-madrid-muon-giu-chan-luka-modric.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Luka Modric</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Luka Modric. Inter Milan \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ch\u00e8o k\u00e9o ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia song \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n anh b\u1eb1ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ronaldo th\u00fac gi\u1ee5c ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn Juventus</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t mong mu\u1ed1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i c\u0169 v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft \u1edf Real, Marcelo gia nh\u1eadp Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5306","checkdouble":"194130"},{"date":"05:59 10/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 10/8: Mourinho \u0111i\u00ean ti\u1ebft v\u00ec b\u1ecb ph\u00eda Godin l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/9/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-108-mourinho-dien-tiet-vi-bi-phia-godin-loi-dung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0110\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p trong m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 10/8.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho \u0111i\u00ean ti\u1ebft v\u00ec b\u1ecb ph\u00eda Godin l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24hvn s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 108 - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin bongda24hvn s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 108 - Tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/mu-nhan-don-dau-tren-ttcn.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Diego Godin</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u01b0\u1edfng ch\u1eebng nh\u01b0 \u201cch\u1ebft \u0111u\u1ed1i v\u1edb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ecdc\u201d khi l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alderweireld, Maguire, Mina hay Boateng tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, sau c\u00f9ng th\u00ec MU c\u0169ng ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Godin m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 m\u1eddi g\u1ecdi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9, k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 18 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, HLV Jose Mourinho t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 t\u00ecnh l\u1ea5y \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ra l\u00e0m b\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea1p \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap anh c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi k\u00fd k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Atletico Madrid tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 7,5 tri\u1ec7u Euro/n\u0103m.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 s\u00e1u ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c r\u1eddi MU trong ng\u00e0y deadline<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 108 Mourinho \u0111i\u00ean ti\u1ebft v\u00ec b\u1ecb ph\u00eda Godin l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng 108 Mourinho \u0111i\u00ean ti\u1ebft v\u00ec b\u1ecb ph\u00eda Godin l\u1ee3i d\u1ee5ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/8/7/Diem-tin-bong-da-sang-108-Mourinho-dien-tiet-vi-bi-phia-Godin-loi-dung-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Timothy Fosu-Mensah</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tu nghi\u1ec7p \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Crystal Palace, Timothy Fosu-Mensah tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 MU nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Jose Mourinho ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n tin t\u01b0\u1edfng. Th\u1ebf l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5p Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u0111ang r\u1ed1i ren v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1, t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb 20 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi H\u00e0 Lan v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i chia tay CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n v\u00e0 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Fulham theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Fosu-Mensah l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 s\u00e1u r\u1eddi Man Utd trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, sau hai th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Sam Johnstone v\u00e0 Joel Pereira c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ba h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Daley Blind, Cameron Borthwick-Jackson v\u00e0 Axel Tuanzebe. K\u1ebb \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ti\u1ebfp trong ba tu\u1ea7n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a th\u00e1ng T\u00e1m n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u1edf Anh \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh trong ng\u00e0y deadline<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Daniel Arzani: Melbourne City \u2013 Manchester City, cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c \u1edf Celtic<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Mateo Kovacic: Real Madrid \u2013 Chelsea, cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Lucas Perez: Arsenal \u2013 West Ham, 7 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Leander Dendoncker: Anderlecht \u2013 Wolverhampton, cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kovacic toi Chelsea\" title=\"Kovacic toi Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Kovacic-toi-Chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Mateo Kovacic</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Bernard: Shakhtar Donetsk \u2013 Everton, mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Carlos Sanchez: Fiorentina \u2013 West Ham, kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Jordan Ayew: Swansea \u2013 Crystal Palace, cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Caglar Soyuncu: Freiburg \u2013 Leiceter, 19 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Harry Arter: Bournemouth \u2013 Cardiff, cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"West Ham mua thanh cong Lucas Perez\" title=\"West Ham mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Lucas Perez\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Diem-tin-Bong-da-24h-toi-ngay-0908-Harry-Maguire-chac-chan-den-MU-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Lucas Perez</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Federico Fernandez: Swansea \u2013 Newcastle, 6 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Luciano Vietto: Atletico Madrid \u2013 Fulham, cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Yerry Mina: Barcelona \u2013 Everton, 27 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Andre Gomes: Barcelona \u2013 Everton, cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Yerry Mina va Andre Gomes\" title=\"Yerry Mina v\u00e0 Andre Gomes\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/10/gettyimages-1014015780.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Yerry Mina v\u00e0 Andre Gomes</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Timothy Fosu-Mensah: Manchester United \u2013 Fulham, cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Andre-Frank Zambo Anguissa: Marseille \u2013 Fulham, 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Danny Ings: Liverpool \u2013 Southampton, cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5305","checkdouble":"194143"},{"date":"18:50 09/08","title":"Barca \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 Yerry Mina c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 34 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/barca-dong-y-de-yerry-mina-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh-voi-gia-34-trieu-bang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Barca b\u00e1n Yerry Mina cho Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 34 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Mail c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mua h\u1ee5t Mina</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, trung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia v\u1eeba ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Barca b\u00e1n Yerry Mina cho Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 34 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Barca b\u00e1n Yerry Mina cho Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 34 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/5/Barca-ban-Yerry-Mina-cho-Everton-voi-gia-34-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Yerry Mina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Yerry Mina, \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994. T\u1edd Mirror c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng m\u00e0 Man \u0111\u1ecf d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi ra, b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 \u1edf ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i khi M.U t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u1ee5 m\u00e0 Mina v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn M.U, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c, v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Barca \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mina s\u1eafp c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Everton</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-yerry-mina-toi-ngoai-hang-anh-nhung-khong-phai-mu-172-193827.html\" target=\"_blank\">Barca b\u00e1n Yerry Mina cho Everton</span> v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 34 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Daily Mail c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Everton dat duoc thoa thuan mua Mina voi gia 40 trieu bang\" title=\"Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Mina v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/mina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Mina v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 34 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ebfn T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 34 tri\u1ec7u&nbsp;b\u1ea3ng. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 trong \u00edt gi\u1edd t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia, Everton c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3n Andre Gomes c\u0169ng t\u1eeb Barca. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Goodison Park theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Mina v\u00e0 Andre Gomes, \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Everton s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Digne t\u1eeb Barca v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u euro v\u00e0 b\u1ecf ra 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Richarlison.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111ang \u0111\u1eb7t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 5 \u0111\u1ebfn 6 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5304","checkdouble":"194126"},{"date":"19:38 09/08","title":"Thibaut Courtois CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/thibaut-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thibaut Courtois ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn NHM Chelsea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Los Blancos l\u00e0 CLB t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Courtois</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u00e1ng nay, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Thibaut Courtois t\u1eeb Chelsea. Los Blancos \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, h\u1ecd b\u1ecf ra 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c The Blues nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Thibaut Courtois ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Thibaut Courtois ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/CHINH-THUC-Thibaut-Courtois-ra-mat-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois \u0111\u1ebfn Real v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean Real c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m. Courtois sau \u0111\u00f3 ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c di chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u1ec3 ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f2i r\u1eddi Chelsea t\u1edbi Real, anh mu\u1ed1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Madrid g\u1ea7n g\u0169i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. The Blues r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i s\u1ee9c \u00e9p t\u1eeb Courtois v\u00e0 Real khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi Chelsea ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge kh\u00f4ng thu v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Chelsea</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/chinh-thuc-kovacic-gia-nhap-chelsea-theo-dang-cho-muon-172-194070.html\" target=\"_blank\">Thibaut Courtois ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</span>, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 khi\u1ebfn NHM Chelsea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Los Blancos l\u00e0 CLB t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thibaut Courtois ra mat Real Madrid\" title=\"Thibaut Courtois ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/thibaut-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thibaut Courtois ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cH\u00f4m nay t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid, khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi m\u1eddi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cC\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ch\u00fat r\u1eafc r\u1ed1i v\u1edbi Chelsea nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 \u1ed5n. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh cho Real, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn. Th\u1eddi gian ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng t\u1ea1i Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadp trung to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c gi\u00fap Real thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCourtois nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Navas \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Real \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111ang \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao, \u1edf World Cup 2018 anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5303","checkdouble":"194131"},{"date":"20:53 09/08","title":"Coutinho CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C k\u1ebf th\u1eeba s\u1ed1 \u00e1o c\u1ee7a huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Figo","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/coutinho-chinh-thuc-ke-thua-so-ao-cua-huyen-thoai-figo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Philippe Coutinho kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 \u1edf Barca t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb s\u1ed1 \u00e1o 14 \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y s\u00e1ng s\u1ed1 7 \u1edf m\u00f9a 2018/19.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Coutinho m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 14 khi m\u1edbi t\u1edbi Barca</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua, Barca \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Philippe Coutinho t\u1eeb Liverpool. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 \u1edf H\u00e8 2017 song The Kop \u0111\u00e3 ki\u00ean quy\u1ebft t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Philippe Coutinho kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 \u1edf Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Philippe Coutinho kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 \u1edf Barca h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Philippe-Coutinho-khoac-ao-so-7-o-Barca-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Coutinho \u0111eo \u00e1o s\u1ed1 14 khi m\u1edbi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Barca</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn phi\u00ean ch\u1ee3 \u0110\u00f4ng 2018, sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c Barca \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra t\u1edbi 160 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCoutinho l\u00e0 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong nh\u1eefng n\u0103m g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 to\u00e0n n\u0103ng khi ghi b\u00e0n hay ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Barca.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou, Coutinho kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 14. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f3 hi\u1ec3u b\u1edfi anh \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 m\u00e0 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 14 \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Coutinho quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay \u0111\u1ed5i s\u1ed1 \u00e1o</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Philippe Coutinho kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 \u1edf Barca t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb s\u1ed1 \u00e1o 14 \u1edf m\u00f9a n\u00e0y s\u00e1ng s\u1ed1 7 \u1edf m\u00f9a 2018/19.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Coutinho khoac ao so 7 o Barca tu mua giai toi\" title=\"Coutinho kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 \u1edf Barca t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/coutinho.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Coutinho kho\u00e1c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 \u1edf Barca t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00c1o s\u1ed1 7 do ti\u00ea\u0300n v\u00ea\u0323 Arda Turan \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i, l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh s\u1ed1 \u00e1o n\u00e0y khi m\u1edbi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua, Barca \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Antoine Griezmann c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid, h\u1ecd th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ec3 d\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay khi m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, Coutinho \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ecf \u00fd mu\u1ed1n m\u1eb7c \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi v\u00e0 Barca \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd. Chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7 g\u1eafn li\u1ec1n v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou, bao g\u1ed3m Luis Figo (1995-2000), Eidur Gudjohnsen (2006-2010) hay David Villa (2010-2013).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCoutinho v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng Brazil, anh v\u00e0 Selecao \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9 \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Hi\u1ec7n c\u1ef1u sao Liverpool \u0111ang t\u1eadp trung c\u00f9ng Barca \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5302","checkdouble":"194134"},{"date":"22:31 09/08","title":"Atletico Madrid CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u1edbi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/atletico-madrid-chinh-thuc-co-tien-dao-moi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Atletico Madrid mua Nikola Kalinic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 13 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a AC Milan.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Atletico quan t\u00e2m Nikola Kalinic</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, AC Milan g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c khi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gonzalo Higuain t\u1eeb Juventus, s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina khi\u1ebfn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Nikola Kalinic b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Atletico Madrid mua Nikola Kalinic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Atletico Madrid mua Nikola Kalinic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/2/CHINH-THUC-Atletico-Madrid-mua-Nikola-Kalinic-thanh-cong-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nicola Kalinic \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Atletico quan t\u00e2m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ee7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a AC Milan v\u1edbi h\u01a1n 30 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Serie A, song anh s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb khi Higuain c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf s\u00e2n San Siro. Bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 30 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/atletico-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-tien-dao-moi-180-193893.html\" target=\"_blank\">Atletico Madrid quan t\u00e2m Nikola Kalinic</span>, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Kevin Gameiro ra \u0111i. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o danh s\u00e1ch thanh l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nValencia \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kevin Gameiro, ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n Atletico mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Nikola Kalinic h\u1ecd s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ea9y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ra \u0111i. Sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n mua Kalinic, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Atletico mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Kalinic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Atletico Madrid mua Nikola Kalinic th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 13 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a AC Milan.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nikola Kalinic chinh thuc gia nhap Atletico Madrid\" title=\"Nikola Kalinic ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Atletico Madrid\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/atletico-madrid-chinh-thuc-co-tien-dao-moi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nikola Kalinic ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c gia nh\u1eadp Atletico Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn: \u201cAtletico de Madrid v\u00e0 AC Milan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 30 tu\u1ed5i Nikola Kalinic. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cKalinic l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u00f3 chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n t\u1ed1t, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1edf h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m. Kalinic l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho Atletico, hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp nhanh nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u00e0 nhanh ch\u00f3ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i ghi 33 b\u00e0n sau 84 tr\u1eadn trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Fiorentina, anh c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn AC Mian v\u00e0o H\u00e8 2017. M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 ch\u1ec9 ghi 6 b\u00e0n sau 31 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n \u1edf Serie A. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG anh c\u00f3 15 b\u00e0n sau 42 tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede World Cup 2018, v\u1edbi h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i ra s\u00e2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng l\u01b0ng Kalinic \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb HLV Dalic \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm. H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i khi\u1ebfn anh m\u1ea5t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u1ea7m tr\u1ecdng trong m\u1eaft NHM Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5301","checkdouble":"194137"},{"date":"22:17 09/08","title":"Thibaut Courtois khi\u1ebfn Chelsea cay c\u00fa","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/19/thibaut-courtois-khien-chelsea-cay-cu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Thibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Courtois mu\u1ed1n Hazard t\u1edbi Real</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y v\u00e0i gi\u1edd, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Courtois \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft Real Madrid. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Madrid, anh \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1ea3i qua y t\u1ebf v\u00e0 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Courtois Hazard\" title=\"Courtois Hazard\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/10/12/thich-the-hien-hazard-bi-dong-doi-chelsea-mang-te-tat.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Courtois mu\u1ed1n Hazard t\u1edbi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;N\u1ebfu anh \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn Real Madrid, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. Hazard h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi t\u00f4i c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid, anh \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00fac m\u1eebng t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i v\u00e0 Hazard l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ed1t, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac n\u1ebfu anh \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh m\u00ecnh \u1edf Real&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft Real mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Hazard, anh \u1ea5y c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Bernabeu. T\u00f4i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 6 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Real, t\u00f4i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t hy v\u1ecdng anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai g\u1ea7n&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Courtois khi\u1ebfn NHM Chelsea kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt NHM c\u1ee7a The Blues \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Courtois gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/thibaut-courtois-chinh-thuc-ra-mat-real-madrid-180-194131.html\" target=\"_blank\"> Courtois c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real Madrid</span>, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Bernabeu v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real, Thibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"C\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Real, Thibaut Courtois ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Cap-ben-Real,-Thibaut-Courtois-phat-bieu-ve-Eden-Hazard-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Thibaut Courtois gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch l\u00fd do t\u1ea1i sao ch\u1ecdn Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi Real v\u00ec ti\u1ec1n, t\u00f4i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Real b\u1edfi t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ea7n g\u0169i v\u1edbi c\u00e1c con c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i gia \u0111\u00ecnh r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bernabeu&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;H\u00f4m nay t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid, hy v\u1ecdng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd nhanh ch\u00f3ng h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ea1nh tranh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5300","checkdouble":"194138"},{"date":"22:54 09/08","title":"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 chia tay Chelsea","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-them-mot-cau-thu-chia-tay-chelsea.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jay Dasilva r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bristol City theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, HLV Lee Johnson c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a The Blues.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jay Dasilva kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Jay Dasilva c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn l\u00f2 \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Chelsea n\u0103m 13 tu\u1ed5i, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn nay anh tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Tuy nhi\u00ean, v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn, r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jay Dasilva r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bristol City theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jay Dasilva r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bristol City theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/Jay-Dasilva-roi-Chelsea-cap-ben-Bristol-City-theo-dang-cho-muon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jay Dasilva kh\u00f3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, HLV Conte \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ea9y Jay Dasilva t\u1edbi Charlton Athletic theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 m\u00f9a, trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Charlton c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n t\u1edbi 48 l\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh c\u0169ng \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, nh\u01b0ng anh kh\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ra \u0111i theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, nh\u1eb1m gi\u00fap anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Jay Dasilva ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Bristol City</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jay Dasilva r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bristol City theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, HLV Lee Johnson c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i H\u1ea1ng nh\u1ea5t Anh t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi m\u01b0\u1ee3n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a The Blues.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jay Dasilva r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bristol City theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Jay Dasilva r\u1eddi Chelsea c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bristol City theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/chinh-thuc-them-mot-cau-thu-chia-tay-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jay Dasilva chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Bristol City theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui m\u1eebng khi Jay Dasilva ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bristol City, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong th\u1eddi gian kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Bristol City theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Bristol City, Jay Dasilva s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t anh s\u1ebd c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJay Dasilva t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c U16, U17, U18, U19 v\u00e0 U20 Anh, NHM Chelsea \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 s\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bristol City theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5299","checkdouble":"194139"},{"date":"23:16 09/08","title":"Yerry Mina CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/9/yerry-mina-chinh-thuc-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Yerry Mina r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park. Barca \u0111\u00e3 thu v\u1ec1 30,2 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Everton chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Mina</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 Yerry Mina \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt \u1edf World Cup 2018, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 gi\u00fap anh nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Yerry Mina r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Yerry Mina r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/yerry-mina-chinh-thuc-cap-ben-ngoai-hang-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mina ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Everton</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-ca-nhan-voi-mina-172-193764.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Mina</span>, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 v\u00ec Man \u0111\u1ecf kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n ph\u1ee5 m\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia y\u00eau c\u1ea7u.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nEverton sau \u0111\u00f3 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m trong vi\u1ec7c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i. S\u1ef1 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c v\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 nghi\u00eam t\u00fac \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Everton c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, Yerry Mina r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 5 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park. Barca \u0111\u00e3 thu v\u1ec1 30,2 tri\u1ec7u euro t\u1eeb th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 th\u00eam 1.5 tri\u1ec7u euro ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p c\u1ee7a Mina. Barca c\u0169ng k\u00e8m theo \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u01b0u ti\u00ean mua l\u1ea1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mina l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi Everton</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Barca ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra 11,8 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Mina t\u1eeb Palmeiras, ch\u1ec9 sau v\u00e0i th\u00e1ng h\u1ecd b\u00e1n ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh cho Everton v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 30,2 tri\u1ec7u euro. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf s\u00e2n Camp Nou, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Everton dat duoc thoa thuan mua Mina voi gia 40 trieu bang\" title=\"Everton \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Mina v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/9/mina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mina l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Everton</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ec1u cao v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i c\u00f9ng kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tranh ch\u1ea5p t\u1ed1t, Mina ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994, Everton \u0111ang cho th\u1ea5y tham v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00e8 n\u00e0y, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 C\u1ea3ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf ra 25 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Digne t\u1eeb Barca v\u00e0 chi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Richarlison t\u1eeb Watford.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, HLV Marco Silva \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o Top 6 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5298","checkdouble":"194140"}]}